snippet.title: Quake Single Player Map: The Purifier
snippet.description:
Download: https://www.quaddicted.com/reviews/purifier.html

Single-player Quake 1 map - "The Purifier" by Zothique (purifier.bsp) utilizing Copper mod 1.15 (including a fix of the upcoming 1.16 version)

This is the Temple of the Neopuritan and purge of civilizations. House of worship, industry of the spirit. Offer your blood upon the altars of the New Doctrine or be drowned in cold gallons of those who did not want to embrace it. Kneel before the New Gods and be purified in the veins of the great factory-cathedral
